The paper deals with the use of sensor networks for exploration and mapping of unknown environments, which is a topic that falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also utilizes probabilistic motion models and topological data analysis, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY).
